Send a message to an offline queue and handle gracefully? Resend per interval. Demonstrate guaranteed delivery of message data once receiving queue becomes active. Pushes an asynchronous message onto the connectToOfflineEndpoint queue every 15 secs. From the queue an attempt is made to post to http://localhost:8184/cxf/offlineRequest. If it fails the message will remain on the queue and retry every 30secs until successful 
